Heather Glenn - National Account Executive at FM Payments

## Project Overview

This repository contains the source code for Heather Glenn's professional website. The site serves as a virtual business card, showcasing Heather's role as a National Account Executive at FM Payments.

## Features

- Single-page design
- Responsive layout for mobile, tablet, and desktop
- Modern, clean aesthetic with a professional focus
- Smooth scrolling navigation
- Call-to-action for contacting Heather
- Email signup form for updates

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Netlify (for hosting)

## Setup and Deployment

1. Clone this repository to your local machine.
2. Make any necessary changes to the HTML, CSS, or JavaScript files.
3. Commit and push your changes to GitHub.
4. Connect your GitHub repository to Netlify for automatic deployment.

## Local Development

To run this project locally:

1. Open the project folder in your preferred code editor.
2. Use a local server (like Live Server in VS Code) to view the website.
3. Make changes and refresh your browser to see updates.

